body:
Numeric facets have the following syntax:

```json
{
  "$searchMeta": {
    "facet":{
      "operator": {
        <operator-specification>
      },
      "facets": {
        "<facet-name>" : {
          "type" : "number",
          "path" : "<field-path>",
          "boundaries" : <array-of-numbers>,
          "default": "<bucket-name>"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```
